{{Orphan|date=January 2015}} {{Infobox person | name = Ndue Përlleshi | image = Photograph of Ndue Perlleshi.jpg | alt = | caption = Photo of Ndue Përlleshi | birth_date = 1908 <!-- {{Birth date|1840}} --> | birth_place = [[Paskalice Village,Lug Te Drinit]],<ref>http://www.shkoder.net/fjala/2003/tmrijaj2.htm</ref> (in modern-day, [[Kosova]]) | death_date = August, 29th,1949 | death_place = Iballe, [[Albania]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://bkdsh.de.tl/Ndue-Perlleshi.htm|title=Besëlidhja Kombëtare Demokratike Shqiptare - Ndue Perlleshi|website=bkdsh.de.tl|accessdate=21 September 2017}}</ref> | nationality = [[Albanians|Albanian]] | other_names = | known_for = Commander of the [[Dukagjini Band]] during [[World War II]] | occupation = }}
'''Ndue Përlleshi''', (1908–1949), was a Kosovar-Albanian military leader, local and national hero, known as "Trimi I Dukagjinit".<ref>{{cite web|url=https://books.google.com/books/about/Ndue_P%C3%ABrlleshi_Trimi_i_Dukagjinit.html?id=s7yPtwAACAAJ|title=Ndue Përlleshi - Trimi i Dukagjinit: (monografi)|first=Jetish|last=Kadishani|date=21 September 2017|publisher=Drenusha|accessdate=21 September 2017|via=Google Books}}</ref> He was the Commander of the "Dukagjini Band" during [[World War II]]. In Mars 8, 1948, during the Battle of Bokshiq, Ndue Perlleshi, along Shaban Dema and Ndrec Nikolla, fought Montenegrin and Albanian communist forces numbering 600. Perlleshi killed 27 communists, and wounded many others, and both his comrades died. He survived with four wounds and returned to his home until Janko Boric, the local community leader, spotted him and threw a grenade through his window. Perlleshi quickly grabbed it and tossed it back to Boric wounding him. Ndue Perlleshi was killed on August 29, 1949 in Albania by the communist forces of Mehmet Shehu. Ndue Perlleshi is a much honoured hero amongst the Albanians of [[Dukagjin highlands|Dukagjin]] and [[District of Peć|Peja]]-region. He is mentioned in Albanian epic folklore.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.trepca.net/2003/0703/030718-tm-nacionalisti-ndue.perlleshi.htm|title=Nacionalisti Ndue Perlleshi (1908-1949) ra dëshmor me ëndrrën e pashuar për Shqiperinë Etnike|website=www.trepca.net|accessdate=21 September 2017}}</ref>
